data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!!  PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!!  Owning this home is a fantastic opportunity to bring your creative vision to life! This spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom single-family home is priced to sell for someone willing to put in a little sweat equity.  It is located less than a mile from I-4. With its prime location and ample potential, this fixer-upper gem is just waiting to be transformed into your dream residence.    Key Features:  - This home boasts ample space for comfortable living and the potential to create your ideal home office, guest room, or hobby space.  - Unleash your inner designer and reimagine this home's layout and aesthetics to match your unique style. Whether you're looking to embrace a modern, rustic, or traditional design, the possibilities are endless.  - Situated on a generous lot, this property provides plenty of outdoor space for gardening, entertaining, or even the addition of a pool.  - The property's prime location offers convenient access to shopping, dining, schools, and parks, making it an ideal spot for families or those seeking a well-connected community.  - With a little TLC, this fixer-upper has the potential to become a valuable investment, whether you're planning to make it your forever home or to renovate and resell.    Don't miss out on the chance to turn this diamond in the rough into a true masterpiece. Imagine the possibilities and take the first step towards creating the home you've always envisioned. Seize this opportunity and schedule a showing today!  All potential buyers are required to view the home before making an offer.  Sellers are motivated!!
